parameters:
\SE[38]I tried to imitate the miracle of Nagi in my own
way. \!\SE[37]It is far more clumsy compared to that...
\!\SE[38]But it is sufficient to create a battlefield with
no escape route.

\SE[2]Surprisingly, you're quite considerate. \SE[1]Even if
you didn't do that, I wouldn't run away.

\SE[0]...That might be true. \SE[2]The aura surrounding you
is different from before. \SE[2]It seems like you've been
through some intense battles.

\SE[38]Well, shall we begin? \.At this point, words don't
hold much meaning.

\SE[39]If you die here... I will be the one to save Lunaroa
in your place. \SE[38]The first thing that awakened person
will see is your head.

\SE[37]I wonder what expression you will make...?
\SE[13]Will you hold hatred towards me...? Or will you
lament your own weakness...?

\SE[56]So, even if I lose, you'll save Luna, right?
\SE[1]Hehe... You're quite popular. Luna is...

\SE[14]Hahaha...!! You've truly developed a good eye....
\SE[37]Interesting...! Show me. \SE[38]That strength of
yours...!!

\SE[20]Wait for me... Luna.... \!\SE[1]I'll come to get you
soon...!!
